-- MOVES-BNP Paribas Investment Partners names head of pension fund segment
-- By Ankush Sharma in Bangalore
-- Fri Oct 10, 2014 05:56AM EDT
-- None



Oct 10 (Reuters) - BNP Paribas Investment Partners (BNPP IP), the asset management arm of BNP Paribas SA <BNPP.PA>, has appointed Susan Gostick as the head of its pension fund segment for its institutional business line.

Gostick will be responsible for developing BNPP IP's growth in pensions in major markets globally and will be based in London.